## Non-negotiables

- Task → `completed` only after end-to-end verification, not just a green build (`ship-verification.md`).
- Don't hand-edit lockfiles, `status.json` health, or `.claude/hooks/*` (hook-blocked).
- Don't add an always-loaded rule when a hook or a path-scoped (`paths:`) rule would do — every always-loaded line taxes every turn. Run `/context-budget` if this file or the rules grow.
